			<a href="index.html"><img src="~/ThanhDat/images/logo.png" alt="" /></a>
		</div>
		<div class="cart">
			<p>
				Welcome to our Online Store! <span>Cart:</span><div id="dd" class="wrapper-dropdown-2">
					0 item(s) - $0.00
